WorkItem.Description:
According to the latest DOMCore spec MutationObserver() takes a callback parameter:

https://dvcs.w3.org/hg/domcore/raw-file/tip/Overview.html#mutation-observers

var observer = new MutationObserver(callback)

But in lib.d.ts the constructor takes no arguments:

declare var MutationObserver: {
    prototype: MutationObserver;
    new (): MutationObserver;
}
